description:
Voca is a VoIP communication app offering unrivalled call quality and record low call rates to landlines and mobiles around the world and there are no connection fees. Voca features revolutionary technology ensuring unparalleled call quality and reliability. Voca is the solution for people and business professionals who are tired of underperforming VoIP-apps.

Synchronize your phone book with Voca and you will automatically be shown which of your friends you can call and text for free. Voca also comes with a range of great features intended to make your communication easier and better:

• Call landlines and mobiles around the world at record low rates and no connection fees.
• Free app to app calls — invite friends to call them for free.
• Send texts, images, video — a complete instant messaging service.
• Fully encrypted app-app calls and texts.
• Multiple device support enabling you to use the same account on both your mobile and tablet. 
• Personalization — customise the start page and select the color you like.
• Multiple contact lists — why not create one with your family and one for co-workers.
• 100% ad free — now and always.

This is just the start. Look out for many more useful and cool features to come in the near future. Visit our site to read more and follow us on Twitter for updates and news:

Site — http://www.getvoca.com
Twitter — http://www.twitter.com/getvoca
